snippet.title: Forkscythe v0.5.0: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Forkscythe, a retro FPS unlike any other. Set in a nightmarish world overrun by attacking skulls, you'll need quick reflexes and strategic thinking to survive!

WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2267350
